originalText.text: Chelsea Moving & Storage Company was a great experience for me! Their staff movers were extremely diligent and professional. What I admired most is that they handled all my items with precision, care and diligence. They are easy to work and communicate with, and I felt a level of security with them that I haven't felt with others. A must check out as they are reliable and great at what they do. A definite loyal customer now, so glad I was referred to them by a good friend. If you need storage or moving a definitely recommend as a business worth looking into. Go CM&S!!! ❤️

originalText.text: Amazing service! The movers were right on time, very fast and professional! I also haven’t expected the rate to be the same as we agreed, it is usually higher that quoted, but here we’ve payed the exact amount with no hidden fees. Very grateful to Chelsea movers to have this done so easily!

originalText.text: We can't say enough positive comments about this moving company. We had a particular crazy move out-of-state with not only a full 3-bedroom apartment, but 3 storage units. Donovan and Naomi came up with a realistic plan and the entire crew executed everything beautifully. We were so pleased with their professionalism and responsiveness. We knew we were in good hands. Our possessions arrived safe and sound and on time. This is the third time Chelsea Moving helped us to move. We highly recommend them. Top notch!

originalText.text: Donovan and his crew are the absolute best. Both times I’ve worked with him now, not only has he been reliable, but I feel truly taken care of. Moving can be super stressful and Donovan brings an energy of calm and “we’ve got this”, the exact energy that is needed during a move. In terms of logistics, they have everything you could need, and are patient and so caring with each item. Hire these guys, they will become “your moving guy”, I guarantee it!

originalText.text:
We have used Chelsea for 3 moves both local and long distance. This is an outstanding company. Very responsive, very careful, on time, pleasant people. Naomi in the office is terrific!! Victor as well. Highly recommend. Wouldn't use anyone else.

UPDATE:
We have now used Chelsea for 4 moves. This one moving from NYC to Boston. Donovan and the crew were there on time on a Wednesday. Packed up a 2 bedroom apartment and piano  without hassle or damage and were in Boston at 8:30 on Thursday morning. Would not use any other company because these guys are simply the best!! Naomi thanks again for your help.
